<br>
The downside is they then expect you to follow them around for the next few reds they try and tackle and get upset when you give them a &quot;Good Hunting&quot; and go on your way.<br>
<br>
As a melee helping people has always been very hard and one reaches the point that you would rather watch them die waiting for a reply to your &quot;Need Help?.&quot; than wade in and get accused of KS.<br>
<br>
One of the problems I have on FV is knowing if I <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> should</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> assist. I generally work on the basis that I am a good cleric and I will help anyone once in case they can be turned from their evil ways, but I am sure there will be those who say &quot;Don't heal him he's an evil&quot;.<br>
